      <p class="eyebrow">WHAT IS EMS?</p>
      <h2 id="ems-title" class="section-title">Electrical muscle stimulation, made simple.</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">
        EMS uses safe, low-frequency impulses through a specialized suit while you perform guided
        movements. The coach controls the intensity and keeps the session aligned with your body,
        fitness level, and goal.
      </p>
      <p class="fine-note">
        EMS is a training method, not a shortcut or a medical promise. It works best with coaching,
        consistency, recovery, and smart nutrition.
      </p>
